  <brief_title>Arterial Stiffness, Wave Reflections and Renal Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Observational Study on the Prognostic Significance (Renal and Cardiovascular) of Arterial Stiffness and Arterial Wave Reflections in Patients With Mild to Moderate Renal Impairment</official_title>
  <sponsors>
